        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Butchart Gardens (Brentwood Bay)</h2>
        <p>North of Victoria in the city of Brentwood Bay are the famous <strong>Butchart Gardens</strong>, a gorgeous collection of well-manicured themed gardens with vibrantly colored flowers and plants, as well as mesmerizing fountains.</p>
        <h3>Victoria Butterfly Gardens</h3>
        <p>Nearby the Butchart Gardens are the Victoria Butterly Gardens, a lush indoor rainforest environment full of stunning tropical plants and creatures, including butterflies, parrots, frogs, iguanas, geckoes, an insectarium, and more.</p>
    </section>


